{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC13_ODI_710.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1f,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Huh? I feel like something's different about the library..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Huh...!? Kyah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "It's too noisy. I want silence."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I apologize. There was a major malfunction with the unit that controls the slags."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x91,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Can't you restore it? If this keeps happening, I won't be able to relax and read my book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "The actual control system, its copy, the spare, the spare's spare, the spare's spare's spare, and one more spare..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "They all seem to be out of order.<CR>Deterioration over time seems to<CR>be the cause."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It has become a serious situation that is causing a major inconvenience to the people who visit this facility."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x93,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure they planned for various situations, but I guess even that wasn't enough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I apologize. I am currently attempting to restore the system."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "That's good. So it's gonna be fixed soon, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I will do my best...to make adequate measures."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "M-Ms. Odelia, why are you looking off in a daze?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Let her be. With all the malfunctions, the load of her responsibilities is probably too heavy for her right now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x117,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "...To be honest, I have no prospects for an adequate solution."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I thought so. Tell us the situation."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x119,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "If it was just to restore the control system, it would have been possible."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "However, as a safety measure, the control system has been double-locked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "By accessing the two keys in different locations at the same time, the control system can be accessed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "In other words, I cannot do it by myself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then, we'll just need to give you a hand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "May I ask for your help?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "If that's what it takes to secure a peaceful reading environment, I would've done it even if you hadn't asked."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Now that that's decided, explain it to us in more detail."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Somewhere on the lowest floor is the key to the tertiary control panel."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "By pushing in that control panel and dropping the power at the same time..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "The control system can safely be accessed."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I would like to ask you two to handle the control panel on the lowest floor."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Fine. We'll get to that immediately. Are you ready?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Y-Yes. I'll do my best."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, Keith, I am counting on you."
        }
    ]
}